{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7d7a64498b","title":"董必武对石家庄市解放初期镇压反革命工作的指示","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ca2fdbcd01","index":0,"year":1947,"month":11,"day":24,"articleId":"7d7a64498b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"17dcaafc7c","name":"董必武"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4ce3ba8159","type":"title","text":"董必武对石家庄市解放初期镇压反革命工作的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b"},{"id":"fb7ec88686","type":"authors","text":"董必武","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b"},{"id":"6bfdfb65f6","type":"appellation","text":"董必武同志指示：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b"},{"id":"b9fba9670c","type":"paragraph","text":"镇压反革命是一件很重要的事，反革命不镇压倒就不能管理好石家庄，当然，镇压反革命不是只依靠工作人员，而是要依靠与发动群众。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b"},{"id":"d8f7a179f2","type":"paragraph","text":"要经过群众的审讯，组织人民清算，组织人民法庭审判处决。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b"},{"id":"fc09a1c67e","type":"paragraph","text":"工业部门的技术人员，要注意对伪技术人员，不要与对待特务一般看待，如他们不好，工人所痛恨者，且有特务嫌疑者可关起来，慢慢处理，当然，如工人最痛恨者，由群众审讯处决。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b"},{"id":"c4d845800a","type":"paragraph","text":"如私人资本家对他们的机器有破坏者，以反革命论。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b"},{"id":"6cf4fbaa18","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年11月24日陈用文传达）","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b"}],"page":{"id":"2617e855ec","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"7d7a64498b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}